'''Ɛli sadqi Azayku''', ikka tt nn iga yan umara d yan umdyaz [[Iclḥiyn|aclḥiy]] [[Sus|asusiy]]. Ig yan umɣnas [[Imaziɣn|amaziɣ]] bahra mqqurn. Ilul ɣ usggʷass n 1942 ɣ tmazirt igan s wassaɣ Igran n twinkḥit ɣ [[Idrarn n Waṭlas|idrarn n waṭlas]] ɣ [[Tamnaḍt n Tarudant|trudant]] tasga n [[Sus]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]]. 

Ibda tiɣri nns amenzu ɣ tmazirt n Tafangult ikmalt ɣ [[Mrrakc]], fadd ad ikcm s tinml tanamurt n islmadn. Yumẓ aslkin fad ad iddu ayg aslmad ɣ usinan n usmuttg ɣ [[Imi n Tanut]] (1962-1963, 1963-1964). Ɣ usgʷass n.ɣ 1968 Isskar turragt ɣ umezruy ɣ tsdawit n [[Rrbaṭ|Rrbat]]. Amsadaɣ, ussegwas 1969 Ar 1970, Amaɣun (participe) d [[Ahmed Bukus|Aḥmed Bukus]] d [[Brahim Axyyaṭ|Brahim Axiyyaṭ]] ɣ aɣawas n Annall isalmadn, idda s [[Bariz]] ar isskar tamsirdant (leçon) n tmaziɣt ɣ tinml n [[INALCO]], lbda assujd ituragt n Jaques Berques. Ɣ usggwas n 1967, Ɛli sadqi Azayku, Imdra ɣ Tugi n tamsmunt Tamaziɣt ɣ [[Lmɣrib|Lmeṛṛuk]]. Izzuyd dars imzzan ɣ usgʷass1973/1975 igasn assaɣn imaziɣen iqqburn Tillila d Ziri. 

Ɛli sadqi Azayku yura kigan n tullissin ulla timdyazin, Ɛli sadqi Azayku iga amara li ifkan kigan i [[Tutlayt Taclḥit|tutlayt taclḥit]] ula kullu mad i-llan azday s tmaziɣt, Ɛli sadqi Azayku immut ɣ 10 Cutanbir ɣ tmdint n Rrbat 2004 Itumdal ɣ tmazirt nns Igran.

